[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0353","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0353.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0430","title":"Cart32 3.0 expdate 敏感调试信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cart32 3.0 存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 请求后附加 `/expdate` 路径，无需任何身份认证即可访问服务器调试信息，导致系统配置、用户数据等敏感内容暴露。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需特殊权限，仅需网络可达即可利用，影响 Cart32 3.0 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0430"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.967","remediation":"立即升级 Cart32 至 3.1 及以上版本，该版本已移除 /expdate 调试路径。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）配置中禁止访问 /expdate 路径，或通过 URL 重写规则拦截此类请求。建议迁移至仍在维护的购物车系统，因 Cart32 已停止安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95738697301956&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1358","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20019","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0430.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0430","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0430.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0430.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-27gf-ff72-jfqr/GHSA-27gf-ff72-jfqr.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0430.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--efd046f1-024d-4bf2-9072-81