38ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0345.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4bfaecb4-0e8f-4414-a9a8-523f28f28202.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0345.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1161/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0349.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0346","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0346.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0425","title":"L-Soft LISTSERV 1.8 Web Archives 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"L-Soft LISTSERV 1.8 的 Web Archives 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该组件发送特制请求触发溢出，从而在目标服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击门槛较低。受影响的版本为 L-Soft LISTSERV 1.8，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至安全版本或禁用 Web Archives 组件以规避风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0425"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.320","remediation":"立即将 L-Soft LISTSERV 升级至 1.8d 或更高版本（官方公告 Advisory0 对应的修复版本）。当前最新稳定版为 17.5，建议直接升级至最新版。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 IIS/Apache）层面限制对 Web Archives 组件的访问，仅允许可信 IP 范围访问，或在防火墙层面封禁对 LISTSERV Web 端口（默认 80/443）的外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0048.html","http://www.lsoft.com/news/default.asp?item=Advisory0","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1167","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19893","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0425.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0425","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0425.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0425.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Schmidt/CVE-2000-0425.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5984-j2rg-qm7x/GHSA-5984-j2rg-qm7x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0425.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001346.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0346.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0337","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0337.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0335","title":"GNU glibc 域名解析器可预测ID导致DNS查询结果欺骗漏洞","description":"glibc 2.1.3 及更早版本中的 DNS 解析器（resolver）使用可预测的事务 ID（TXID）生成算法，本地攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的伪造 DNS 响应报文，在无需认证的情况下实施 DNS 缓存投毒攻击，劫持域名解析结果。该漏洞影响使用 glibc 2.1.3 的 Linux 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可诱导用户访问恶意站点或截获敏感信息，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.143","remediation":"升级 glibc 至 2.1.4 或更高版本（glibc 2.2 起默认启用随机化 DNS 事务 ID）。对于无法升级的历史系统，可部署本地缓存 DNS 解析器如 dnsmasq 代为发起查询以缓解预测风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1166","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0335","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/1dbe320292d59a7e991f72ba1744c84debd60371/2000/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/35c40c2c96029682f9c3da862749763b6c97e1fb/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-03xx/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0335.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0335.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0337.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0311","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0311.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0378","title":"RedHat Linux pam_console 模块登录设备文件描述符泄露漏洞","description":"RedHat Linux 6.0/6.1/6.2 系统中 pam_console PAM 模块在用户登录时会对设备文件执行 chown 操作，但退出登录后相关设备的文件描述符仍保持打开状态，导致该用户在后续其他用户登录时可嗅探这些设备的输入输出活动。该漏洞危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.2，攻击者需拥有本地登录权限，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露。建议升级至受支持版本或禁用 pam_console 模块。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0378"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:35.513","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 7.0 或更高版本，其中已修复 pam_console 模块在用户注销后未关闭设备文件描述符的问题。如无法升级系统，可修改 /etc/pam.d/ 下相关配置文件，移除 pam_console.so 模块的调用，或限制可登录控制台的用户组仅包含受信任管理员。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0023.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1176","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19900","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0378.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0378","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0378.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0378.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5949-54q2-grjg/GHSA-5949-54q2-grjg.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0378.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bef28ef8-a6b1-4ae5-ae39-677d4184a250.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0311.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0294","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0294.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0303","title":"id Software Quake3 Arena 目录遍历漏洞","description":"id Software 的 Quake III Arena 存在目录遍历漏洞。恶意服务器运营者可向客户端发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制数据包，绕过路径限制，读取或修改客户端文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞源于对服务器下发的文件路径过滤不足，攻击者利用此漏洞可实现文件窃取或恶意文件写入，危害较大。受影响的版本包括 Quake III Arena 及其衍生版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0303"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.143","remediation":"立即升级 Quake 3 Arena 至 1.16 或更高版本，该版本修复了客户端目录遍历漏洞。如无法升级，可在客户端配置中仅连接受信任服务器，并避免自动下载服务器端文件。作为临时缓解措施，可在防火墙或路由器层面限制游戏端口（默认 27960/UDP）的出站连接范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7531","http://www.quake3arena.com/news/index.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1169","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise50.php3"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0294.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0275","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0275.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0332","title":"UltraScripts UltraBoard 1.6 目录遍历漏洞","description":"UltraBoard 1.6 中的 UltraBoard.pl 及 UltraBoard.cgi CGI 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向脚本传入包含 `../` 序列且以空字符结尾的路径名参数，绕过路径过滤限制，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可读取目标服务器上的敏感配置文件或系统文件，危害较大。受影响版本为 UltraBoard 1.6，建议升级至最新版本或部署 Web 应用防火墙进行防护。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0332"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:29.747","remediation":"立即停用 UltraBoard 1.6 并将论坛迁移至活跃维护的替代产品（如 phpBB、Discourse）。如无法立即迁移，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 重写规则拦截包含 `../` 及 null 字节的请求，并移除 UltraBoard.pl/UltraBoard.cgi 的 SUID 权限以降低影响范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1309","http://www.osvdb.org/4065","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1164","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000503091316.99073.qmail%40hotmail.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19890","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0332","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/35c40c2c96029682f9c3da862749763b6c97e1fb/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-03xx/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/1dbe320292d59a7e991f72ba1744c84debd60371/2000/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0332.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0332.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0275.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0275.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0275.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0351","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0351.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0346","title":"Apple AppleShare IP 6.x 信息泄露漏洞","description":"AppleShare IP 6.1 及之后版本存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 Web 服务器发送特制的无效范围（Range）请求，触发服务器返回敏感信息。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可远程触发，影响 AppleShare IP 6.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0346"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:31.557","remediation":"建议立即下载并安装 AppleShare IP 6.3.1 或更高版本（参考 Apple 安全更新 n11670），该版本修复了 Web 服务器对畸形 HTTP Range 请求处理不当的问题。由于 AppleShare IP 已停产，无法升级时应停止该服务的公网暴露，或在防火墙/反向代理层面过滤异常 Range 头的 HTTP 请求，防止敏感信息泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://asu.info.apple.com/swupdates.nsf/artnum/n11670","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1162","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000502133240.21807.qmail%40securityfocus.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0346.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0346","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0346.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0346.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pp76-3w2g-vm3m/GHSA-pp76-3w2g-vm3m.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0346.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--95543076-20db-4837-82c7-9166f71f32e7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0351.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0351.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0299","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0299.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0347","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 NetBIOS 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 系统中的 NetBIOS 协议实现存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的包含空源名称（NULL Source Name）的 NetBIOS 会话请求数据包，可导致目标系统 NetBIOS 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 和 Windows 98 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。由于系统无法正确处理畸形数据包，攻击者只需构造特定网络请求即可触发，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0347"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:31.690","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Windows 95/98 系统，微软未发布官方补丁。建议升级至仍受支持的 Windows 10/11 版本；若无法升级，应在防火墙层面阻断入站 NetBIOS 流量（UDP 137-139、TCP 137-139 及 445 端口），同时在 TCP/IP 高级设置中禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=95737580922397&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1163","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19889","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0347.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0347","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0347.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0347.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1239.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/netbios.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rfparalyze.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0347.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0299.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0296","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0296.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0343","title":"Brecht Claerhout Sniffit 邮件日志记录缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sniffit 0.3.x 的日志记录选项 (-L) 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Sniffit 服务发送特制的超长 MAIL FROM 邮件头触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Sniffit 0.3.6 及 0.3.7 Beta 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，需目标开启 -L 日志记录选项。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0343"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:31.160","remediation":"建议立即升级 Sniffit 至 0.3.7 Beta 之后的安全版本，或彻底停用已停止维护的 Sniffit，改用 tcpdump 或 Wireshark 等活跃维护的替代工具。若暂时无法替换，避免使用 `-L` 日志选项处理来自不可信来源的邮件数据，并限制 Sniffit 的运行用户权限为最低级别（如非 root 专用账户），以降低缓冲区溢出被利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1158","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=200005021736.TAA01991%40ALuSSi","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19888","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0343.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0343","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0343.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0343.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q5jj-xjv6-mqg6/GHSA-q5jj-xjv6-mqg6.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0343.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0296.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0257","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0293","title":"SuSE Linux aaa_base 任意文件删除漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.x 的 aaa_base 组件及早期版本中的 cron.daily 存在文件名处理缺陷，本地攻击者可创建包含空格的恶意文件名存放于 /tmp 目录，当 aaa_base 清理过期临时文件时，将空格错误解析为文件分隔符，导致可删除系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 6.3 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，需本地用户权限，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0293"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:24.927","remediation":"升级至 SuSE Linux 7.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可修改 aaa_base 脚本，在处理 /tmp 目录过期文件时对文件名添加引号包裹以防止空格被错误解析，同时限制 aaa_base 的执行权限为 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1130","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19867"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0257.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0123","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0123.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0138","title":"Trinoo/TFN/TFN2K/Stacheldraht/mstream/Shaft 分布式拒绝服务代理漏洞","description":"该漏洞指目标系统被植入了分布式拒绝服务（DDoS）攻击工具，包括 Trinoo、Tribe Flood Network（TFN）、Tribe Flood Network 2000（TFN2K）、stacheldraht、mstream 或 shaft 等攻击程序的主控端（master）、代理端（agent）或傀儡端（zombie）。攻击者利用这些工具，通过主控端统一调度大量被控主机同时向指定目标发送海量流量或畸形数据包，从而耗尽目标的网络带宽、系统资源或连接数，导致目标服务瘫痪、无法响应正常请求。受影响系统一旦被感染，便沦为攻击者发动大规模 DDoS 攻击的跳板，攻击条件为系统已被入侵并成功安装相应攻击组件，危害等级为中等，CVSS 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0138"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:04.757","remediation":"立即排查并清理系统中是否安装了 Trinoo、TFN、TFN2K、stacheldraht、mstream、shaft 等 DDoS 攻击工具/代理程序，彻底清除僵尸进程并修复被利用的系统漏洞。部署网络层 DDoS 防护设备（如防火墙、流量清洗设备），配置入侵检测系统拦截 DDoS 攻击流量，及时安装系统安全补丁防止被植入攻击代理。配置防火墙限制异常流量，启用入侵检测系统监控异常流量模式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95715370208598&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95722093124322&w=2","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise48.php3","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0138.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0138","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0138.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0138.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/247.txt","https://github.com/universal-ctags/ctags/blob/5437fa6249e95ec55a5f4944dac28f4f6e46c195/Units/review-needed.r/too-large-for-reviewing-3526726.tex.t/input.tex","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6w6r-f2f7-xh5j/GHSA-6w6r-f2f7-xh5j.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/doc/faq.tex","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/234.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/T/trinity.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0123.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0359","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0359.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0440","title":"FreeBSD/NetBSD 未对齐 IP 时间戳选项拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.4.2 及更早版本、FreeBSD 3.4/4.0/5.0 系统中的 IP 协议栈存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标主机发送包含未对齐（unaligned）IP 时间戳选项的恶意数据包，触发内核处理异常，导致系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞利用无需身份认证，攻击门槛低，仅需构造特定畸形 IP 报文即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0440"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:44.310","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 4.0-STABLE 之后的安全更新版本，或升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.3 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在边界防火墙上配置过滤包含 IP Timestamp 选项的异常数据包，或使用 ipfw/pf 规则丢弃此类畸形报文作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0088.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1173","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19896","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0440.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0440","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0440.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0440.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-3fw7-2f85-c369/GHSA-3fw7-2f85-c369.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--55ba3501-8aef-42cc-a283-cb7ca217a369.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0440.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--55ba3501-8aef-42cc-a283-cb7ca217a369.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0359.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0347","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0347.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0344","title":"Linux Kernel NFS Server knfsd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2.x 系列版本的 NFS 服务组件 knfsd 存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统 NFS 服务发送恶意构造的负数值（negative size）请求，触发 knfsd 处理异常，导致服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.1/2.2/2.3 系列版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0344"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:31.287","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.16 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 2.2.16 中修复），或在 knfsd 配置中限制客户端来源，通过 iptables 限制对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）的访问仅允许可信 IP 段。如无法升级内核，可在 /etc/exports 中使用 secure 选项并禁用匿名写入权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1160","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.21.0005012042550.6419-100000%40ferret.lmh.ox.ac.uk","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0344.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0344","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0344.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0344.json","https://github.com/bell-sw/osv-database/blob/804aa1ae310cecbada28b2df56bdd9c0826a96b6/BELL-CVE/BELL-CVE-2000-0344.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p8m9-pjr4-qwm7/GHSA-p8m9-pjr4-qwm7.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/knfs_dos.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0344.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0347.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0291","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0291.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0341","title":"Atrium Software Cassandra NNTP Server 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ATRIUM Cassandra NNTP Server 1.10 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向登录认证功能提交超长用户名，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Cassandra NNTP Server 1.10 版本，攻击无需身份认证，通过网络即可实施，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0341"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.910","remediation":"` tags.<value>升级 Atrium Software Cassandra NNTP Server 至 1.10 以上版本，或更换为仍受支持的 NNTP 服务软件（如 INN）。如无法升级，应在防火墙层面限制对 NNTPServer 端口（默认 119）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=95736106504870&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1156","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19884","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0341.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve